That empire , after Rome was barbarous , still embraced the nations whom she had conquered beyond the Adriatic , and as far as the frontiers of Aethiopia and Persia . 
The annual powers of vegetation , instead of being exhausted by two thousand harvests , were renewed and invigorated by skilful husbandry , rich manure , and seasonable repose . 
The breed of domestic animals was infinitely multiplied . 
Plantations , buildings , and the instruments of labor and luxury , which are more durable than the term of human life , were accumulated by the care of successive generations . 
