Anthemius formed the design , and his genius directed the hands of ten thousand workmen , whose payment in pieces of fine silver was never delayed beyond the evening . 
The emperor himself , clad in a linen tunic , surveyed each day their rapid progress , and encouraged their diligence by his familiarity , his zeal , and his rewards . 
