, years before the same aera . 
Theophrastus chief of the Peripatetics , and disciple of Aristotle , was involved in the same exile . 
His sagacious mind explored the deepest questions of morals and metaphysics , and he ventured to urge eighteen arguments against the Christian doctrine of the creation of the world . 
From this journey , however , they derived a benefit which reflects the purest lustre on the character of Chosroes . 
The writings of Simplicius are now extant . 
This is no fanciful aera the Pagans reckoned their calamities from the reign of their hero . 
