The epistle of Belisarius to the emperor announced his victory , his danger , and his resolution . 
Hitherto we have successfully fought against the multitudes of the Barbarians , but their multitudes may finally prevail . 
Victory is the gift of Providence , but the reputation of kings and generals depends on the success or the failure of their designs . 
Permit me to speak with freedom if you wish that we should live , send us subsistence if you desire that we should conquer , send us arms , horses , and men . 
For myself , my life is consecrated to your service it is yours to reflect , whether my death in this situation will contribute to the glory and prosperity of your reign . 
