I am not disposed either to question or to justify their Scandinavian origin nor to pursue the migrations of the Lombards through unknown regions and marvellous adventures . 
The smallness of their numbers was recruited by the adoption of their bravest slaves and alone , amidst their powerful neighbors , they defended by arms their high spirited independence . 
Their manners were not less ferocious . 
Their strength was formidable , since the Lombards , who sent into the field several myriads of soldiers , still claimed , as the weaker side , the protection of the Romans . 
