M. ! ! The Negus is differently called Elesbaan , Elesboas , Elisthaeus , probably the same name , or rather appellation . 
Abrahah was a Christian he built a magnificent church at Sana , and dissuaded his subjects from their accustomed pilgrimages to Mecca . 
The church was defiled , it was supposed , by the Koreishites , and Abrahah took up arms to revenge himself on the temple at Mecca . 
The revolt of Abrahah is mentioned by Procopius and his fall , though clouded with miracles , is an historical fact . 
