He proposed a treaty solicited a reconciliation and offered to bind himself by the most solemn oaths . 
By what oaths can he bind himself ? interrupted the indignant Moors . 
Before we trust them a second time , let us try their efficacy in the chastisement of perjury and the vindication of their own honor . 
Their honor was vindicated in the field of Tebeste , by the death of Solomon , and the total loss of his army . 
