The designs of Antonina were favored by the fluctuating jurisprudence of Justinian . 
Before the departure of Belisarius , Perusia was besieged , and few cities were impregnable to the Gothic arms . 
Three thousand of the bravest soldiers had been left to defend the capital . 
The siege of Rome would perhaps have been raised , if the liberality of Totila to the Isaurians had not encouraged some of their venal countrymen to copy the example of treason . 
