The Decemvirs had been named , and their tables were approved , by an assembly of the centuries , in which riches preponderated against numbers . 
But the tribunes soon established a more specious and popular maxim , that every citizen has an equal right to enact the laws which he is bound to obey . 
A new method of secret ballot abolished the influence of fear and shame , of honor and interest , and the abuse of freedom accelerated the progress of anarchy and despotism . 
The Romans had aspired to be equal they were levelled by the equality of servitude and the dictates of Augustus were patiently ratified by the formal consent of the tribes or centuries . 
Once , and once only , he experienced a sincere and strenuous opposition . 
His subjects had resigned all political liberty they defended the freedom of domestic life . 
