For that important work , the emperor Adrian preferred the chief of the Sabinians the friends of monarchy prevailed but the moderation of Salvius Julian insensibly reconciled the victors and the vanquished . 
Like the contemporary philosophers , the lawyers of the age of the Antonines disclaimed the authority of a master , and adopted from every system the most probable doctrines . 
But their writings would have been less voluminous , had their choice been more unanimous . 
An indulgent edict of the younger Theodosius excused him from the labor of comparing and weighing their arguments . 
