Justinian received a free pardon , and the command of the eastern army . 
The Persian monarch fled before his arms and the acclamations which accompanied his triumph declared him worthy of the purple . 
His artful patroness had chosen the month of the vintage , while the emperor , in a rural solitude , was permitted to enjoy the pleasures of a subject . 
On the first intelligence of her designs , he returned to Constantinople , and the conspiracy was suppressed by his presence and firmness . 
