Sophia , and displayed a pathetic spectacle to the people . 
Countrymen and Christians , cried Nicephorus for himself and his mute brethren , behold the sons of your emperor , if you can still recognize our features in this miserable state . 
A life , an imperfect life , is all that the malice of our enemies has spared . 
It is now threatened , and we now throw ourselves on your compassion . 
They were speedily embarked for Greece , and Athens was allotted for the place of their exile . 
