His administration was only the art of satiating his avarice , and Zoe became a captive in the palace of her fathers , and in the hands of her slaves . 
The only act of his short reign was his base ingratitude to his benefactors , the eunuch and the empress . 
For the first time the Greeks beheld with surprise the two royal sisters seated on the same throne , presiding in the senate , and giving audience to the ambassadors of the nations . 
But his health was broken by the tortures of the gout , and his dissolute reign was spent in the alternative of sickness and pleasure . 
